msgid "gluon-config-mode:welcome"
msgstr ""
"Welcome the the setup wizard of your new Freifunk Magdeburg node. Please "
"fill out the following form and transmit it."

msgid "gluon-config-mode:pubkey"
msgstr ""
"This is your Freifunk node's public key. The node won't be able to connect "
"to the mesh network over mesh VPN and share your internet connection until "
"the key has been registered on the Freifunk Magdeburg servers. To register "
"the key enter it together with your node's name (<em><%=hostname%></em>) and "
"some more information at <a href=\"http://register.md.freifunk.net/\">http://"
"register.md.freifunk.net/</a> or directly use this link to <a href=\"http://"
"register.md.freifunk.net/#new?hostname=<%=hostname%>&key=<%=pubkey%>&mac=<%= "
"sysconfig.primary_mac %>\">register your node <em><%=hostname%></em></a>."

msgid "gluon-config-mode:reboot"
msgstr ""
"<p>The node is currently rebooting and will try to connect to other nearby "
"Freifunk nodes  after that. Your can find lots of information about the "
"Freifunk Magdeburg community on <a href=\"https://md.freifunk.net/\">our "
"homepage</a>.</p><p>To get back to this configuration interface, press the "
"reset button for 10 seconds during normal operation. The device will then "
"reboot into config mode.</p><p>Have fun with your node and with exploring "
"the Freifunk network!</p>"
